NOTICE

This project is provided strictly for educational and statistical analysis
purposes. It DOES NOT predict winning lottery numbers, DOES NOT guarantee any
return, and MUST NOT be used to facilitate gambling for minors or in
jurisdictions where such activity is prohibited.

Historical statistics of random events (like lottery draws) cannot predict
future outcomes. Any "recommendation" produced by this tool is a random
suggestion weighted by past frequencies — it does not increase the probability
of winning compared to a uniformly random pick.
